cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CL 

The paper deals with deep metric learning using neural networks for image classification tasks. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of hard example mining and ensembling of models, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. The paper also mentions the use of similarity search (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL) datasets for evaluation.
